      "id": "2034429361139360088",
      "text": "Nick Fuentes is suspicious of Joe Kent and questions what his real goals may be.\n\nIt all about JD Vance.\n\n“This clearly stinks like a play conceived in the vice president’s office. So he can salvage his chances in 2028.”\n\n“This unfolding situation is very convoluted. It gets stranger all the time, and we need to get smart about this.”\n\n“The Joe Kent thing; I’m very suspicious of it. I don’t like it. I think this only serves JD Vance.”",
