      "text": "Nick Fuentes connects Joe Kent, David Sacks, and Tucker Carlson back to Peter Thiel and JD Vance, suggesting something bigger is at play.\n\n“Somebody should ask Tucker, ‘What is your relationship to Peter Thiel?’…they’re far closer than he lets on.”\n\n“Something is going on here…and it’s obvious…they’re making some kind of play.”\n\n“I know you might think I’m being picky. I’m not. You might think I’m being paranoid. I’m not. It’s an op.”\n\n“That’s obviously what’s going on here, and I don’t trust any of these people.”",
