      "text": "Former Director of the National Counterterrorism Center, Joe Kent, suggests Trump was not hearing from key voices like Tulsi Gabbard and JD Vance before starting the war in Iran.\n\n“You had an entire small group that was down there just with the president.”\n\n“While you had the DNI, the Vice President, other key members… far away from those decisions that were being made.”\n\n“The imagery that came out of that night kind of showed you what the president’s tight circle was.”\n\n“Versus some other folks who may have had the ability to offer the president a different perspective.”\n\n@megynkelly @joekent16jan19",
